Renderer API responsible for rendering the video using IMG Texture streaming API.

Note: Set "INST_DEST" in the Makefile to desirable path to install the binary on <TARGET_FILESYSTEM>.

Run the following to build install the binary on to the NULL WINDOW SYSTEM platform -

-  make && make install

Run the following to build and install the binary on to the X-WINDOW SYSTEM platform -

-  make XORG_BUILD=1 && make install

See <documentation>/README for more info.
